data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, full brick home with gorgeous views of fields and forest! Home is full of high end finishings - crown moulding, wainscoting in dining area and hardwoods throughout main living areas. Kitchen flows seamlessly into great room and features beautiful granite counters and plenty of cabinet space! The spa like master suite features a true glamour bath with jetted tub & separate shower. Backyard features covered screened patio & privacy fence. Upstairs bonus room ensuite for teen or playroom. Great location
